<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 04:10:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队准备应对大规模抗议，首批 1,200 名极端正统派男子的传唤日期临近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-gears-for-mass-protests-as-summons-date-for-first-1-200-ultra-orthodox-men-looms/00000191-1dca-d534-a9f9-7dcbf7c30000</link><description>以色列军队预计只有大约 30% 的候选人会参加第一天的面试。在极端正统派社区分发的海报呼吁在征兵办公室进行大规模抗议，“我们现在不会为前 1,000 名而战斗，他们会到达我们所有人，但愿不会，包括你的儿子”</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-gears-for-mass-protests-as-summons-date-for-first-1-200-ultra-orthodox-men-looms/00000191-1dca-d534-a9f9-7dcbf7c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员预计伊朗将袭击军事目标，但以色列中部不再是禁区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-iran-to-attack-military-targets-but-central-israel-is-not-off-limits/00000191-1efd-d68e-a79b-5ffd1a690000</link><description>国防官员预计伊朗和真主党不会收回对以色列暗杀事件进行报复的威胁，以色列可能会面临来自各方的攻击 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡正在拖延时间就人质交易做出决定，美国和以色列官员们越来越沮丧</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-iran-to-attack-military-targets-but-central-israel-is-not-off-limits/00000191-1efd-d68e-a79b-5ffd1a690000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的困境：如何应对以色列暗杀而不自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/irans-dilemma-how-to-respond-to-israels-assassinations-without-committing-suicide/00000191-1f90-d68e-a79b-5f9561330000</link><description>以色列、伊朗和真主党现在陷入了一场屈辱的战争，复仇和威慑的复杂数学很容易被误判并导致全面战争。伊朗知道他们必须对以色列最近的袭击做出回应，但他们如何回应以及接下来会发生什么取决于他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:04:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article/.premium/irans-dilemma-how-to-respond-to-israels-assassinations-without-committing-suicide/00000191-1f90-d68e-a79b-5f9561330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称，来自黎巴嫩的炮火袭击导致军官和士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-says-officer-and-soldier-wounded-after-barrage-from-lebanon/00000191-201c-d534-a9f9-6d1d986b0000</link><description>土耳其敦促其公民离开黎巴嫩 ■ 美国中央司令部司令将于周一在伊朗袭击之前访问以色列 ■ 以色列国防军发言人表示，国防系统“并非严密”，公众必须“保持警惕” ■ 由于局势动荡，英国暂时撤回贝鲁特外交官的家属■ 加沙救援服务：学校罢工死亡人数上升至 30 人</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-says-officer-and-soldier-wounded-after-barrage-from-lebanon/00000191-201c-d534-a9f9-6d1d986b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列游泳运动员戈尔本科无缘奥运会200米决赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-swimmer-gorbenko-misses-out-on-200m-olympics-final/00000191-1edb-d1c6-a591-9edf2c5d0000</link><description>这位以色列奥运选手错过了参加200米个人混合泳的机会，显然是因为她没有收到足够的提前通知。以色列奥委会表示，这一事件“使游泳运动员陷入了不可能的境地”</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-swimmer-gorbenko-misses-out-on-200m-olympics-final/00000191-1edb-d1c6-a591-9edf2c5d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡有能力阻止地区战争——所需要的只是与哈马斯达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-power-to-prevent-a-regional-war-all-it-takes-is-a-deal-with-hamas/00000191-1eb5-d68e-a79b-5fb5ee350000</link><description>与哈马斯的停火协议并不需要就拆除定居点、割让领土或建立巴勒斯坦国进行谈判。它只需要将人质带回家，结束一场持续了近10个月的战争，并有很好的机会防止一场中东从未发生过的大火</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-the-power-to-prevent-a-regional-war-all-it-takes-is-a-deal-with-hamas/00000191-1eb5-d68e-a79b-5fb5ee350000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：由于安全局势，吉迪恩·萨尔加入内塔尼亚胡联盟的谈判被搁置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/sources-talks-on-giden-saar-joining-netanyahu-govt-shelved-due-to-security-situation/00000191-1ea5-d68e-a79b-5fb599cf0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡与新希望党主席之间的间接谈判近几周有所加强，但知情人士表示，和解仍很遥远，萨尔最终是否会加入政府仍不确定</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 19:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/sources-talks-on-giden-saar-joining-netanyahu-govt-shelved-due-to-security-situation/00000191-1ea5-d68e-a79b-5fb599cf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长的两名大学理事会候选人在内阁同意前保释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-ministers-two-candidates-for-college-council-bail-at-last-minute/00000191-1e8c-d5b2-afb7-defc3a860000</link><description>吉迪·萨皮尔（Gidi Sapir）和米里亚姆·费尔伯格-伊卡尔（Miriam Feirberg-Ikar）援引了“个人原因”，但他们在最后一刻做出的决定是在大学校长致总检察长的一封信中警告教育部长约夫·基什（Yoav Kisch）试图夺取高等教育委员会的控制权之后做出的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 18:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-ministers-two-candidates-for-college-council-bail-at-last-minute/00000191-1e8c-d5b2-afb7-defc3a860000</guid></item><item><title>呼吁转移巴勒斯坦人并定居加沙：会见内塔尼亚胡的新发言人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/calling-to-transfer-palestinians-and-settle-gaza-meet-netanyahus-new-spokesperson/00000191-1e4f-d1c6-a591-9e5fcba60000</link><description>奥马尔·多斯特里博士拥有政治学博士学位，他相信“以色列必须下令在其占领的许多地区迅速建立以色列定居点”。在他的新职位上，他将负责总理办公室的通讯部门</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 18:29:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/calling-to-transfer-palestinians-and-settle-gaza-meet-netanyahus-new-spokesperson/00000191-1e4f-d1c6-a591-9e5fcba60000</guid></item><item><title>随着拜登再次拯救以色列，其无能领导人为特朗普竞选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-04/ty-article/.highlight/as-biden-comes-to-israels-rescue-again-its-inept-leaders-campaign-for-trump/00000191-1e26-d5b2-afb7-de7ef1ed0000</link><description>以色列不一定要接受美国的每一项要求，对华盛顿的每一项政策建议都说“是”，但至少，其无能的领导层——导致1200多名以色列人死亡、这是该国历史上最大的失败——应该承担责任。谦虚一点</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-04/ty-article/.highlight/as-biden-comes-to-israels-rescue-again-its-inept-leaders-campaign-for-trump/00000191-1e26-d5b2-afb7-de7ef1ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 303 天：加沙记录的乙型肝炎病例超过 10 万例</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-303-over-100-000-cases-of-hepatitis-b-recorded-in-gaza/00000191-1e43-d68e-a79b-5fd7a4f20001</link><description>两名以色列人在霍隆市的刺伤袭击中丧生，两人中度受伤 ■ 美国高级官员告诉《国土报》，拜登已经意识到内塔尼亚胡在寻求人质释放协议方面向他撒谎 ■ 大特拉维夫地区居民报告 GPS 严重中断 ■ 据报道，伊朗告诉阿拉伯国家外交官们，它并不关心对哈尼亚被杀事件的反应是否会引发地区战争 ■ 战争已经过去 303 天了，以下是你需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:43:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-303-over-100-000-cases-of-hepatitis-b-recorded-in-gaza/00000191-1e43-d68e-a79b-5fd7a4f20001</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党的“火战”：卫星图像揭示了毁灭性的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-and-israels-war-of-fire-satellite-images-reveal-its-devastating-effect/00000191-1dbf-db97-a7df-fdff6c4e0000</link><description>图片显示，自敌对行动爆发以来 — — 但主要是自 5 月以来 — — 以色列和黎巴嫩约 52000 英亩土地被烧毁。以色列的烧焦总面积是以色列历史上两场最大火灾烧毁面积的三倍</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 16:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-and-israels-war-of-fire-satellite-images-reveal-its-devastating-effect/00000191-1dbf-db97-a7df-fdff6c4e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于两国关系紧张，以色列外交部长用土耳其语抨击埃尔多安后走红</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-goes-viral-after-blasting-erdogan-in-turkish-as-ties-between-countries-strain/00000191-1d55-d534-a9f9-7d5ddfa60000</link><description>以色列外长严厉斥责埃尔多安，称土耳其总统支持“杀人犯和强奸犯”，正在“摧毁”土耳其，而以色列和土耳其的关系因加沙战争而持续恶化</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-goes-viral-after-blasting-erdogan-in-turkish-as-ties-between-countries-strain/00000191-1d55-d534-a9f9-7d5ddfa60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前部长的儿子于 10 月 7 日被杀，成为支持内塔尼亚胡的网络仇恨目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-minister-whose-son-was-killed-on-oct-7-targeted-by-pro-netanyahu-online-hate/00000191-1ddb-d1c6-a591-9ddfe8eb0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡前部长伊扎尔·谢伊在因批评以色列政策而受到内塔尼亚胡支持者的辱骂后表示，“我们将与那些心怀恶意的人作斗争，他们瞄准死者家属的家长，希望我和我的孩子都死掉”。下午</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-minister-whose-son-was-killed-on-oct-7-targeted-by-pro-netanyahu-online-hate/00000191-1ddb-d1c6-a591-9ddfe8eb0000</guid></item><item><title>贝都因青少年在攀爬基布兹围栏后被枪杀。他的父亲正在寻求正义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bedouin-teen-was-shot-dead-after-climbing-a-kibbutzs-fence-his-fathers-seeking-justice/00000191-1d00-d534-a9f9-7d0912850000</link><description>一名 18 岁少年被南部基布兹保安队一名涉嫌盗窃的成员杀害。这位年轻人的父亲希望能够告诉他的孩子们，以色列仍然是一个法治国家</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bedouin-teen-was-shot-dead-after-climbing-a-kibbutzs-fence-his-fathers-seeking-justice/00000191-1d00-d534-a9f9-7d0912850000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫和以色列中部报告 GPS 干扰，与 4 月伊朗袭击前夕相呼应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/gps-jamming-reported-in-tel-aviv-and-central-israel-echoing-eve-of-aprils-iran-attack/00000191-1d01-d534-a9f9-7d09a4400000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，GPS 中断在以色列北部已司空见惯，但在特拉维夫却很少见。以色列国防军此前承认，卫星干扰是针对 GPS 制导无人机或导弹的主动措施</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/gps-jamming-reported-in-tel-aviv-and-central-israel-echoing-eve-of-aprils-iran-attack/00000191-1d01-d534-a9f9-7d09a4400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军起诉延长了对涉嫌虐待斯德·泰曼的五名以色列士兵的拘留期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/prosecution-seeks-extended-custody-of-five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-sde-teiman-abuse/00000191-1caf-db97-a7df-fcffecc00000</link><description>以色列国防军法院审查了延长八名嫌疑人还押候审的请求，这些嫌疑人被指控在被俘恐怖分子拘留中心严重虐待一名加沙被拘留者。在听证会上，检方表示，针对五名嫌疑人的证据已得到显着加强</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/prosecution-seeks-extended-custody-of-five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-sde-teiman-abuse/00000191-1caf-db97-a7df-fcffecc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在巴黎奥运会上取得空前成功的秘诀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/the-secret-to-israels-success-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-1d00-da43-afdf-3f229bc00000</link><description>多年的投资让以色列在 2024 年奥运会上寄予厚望，但这些期望在神奇的三天里被超越，以色列获得了六枚奥运会奖牌，其中包括一枚金牌。团队是这样做的</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 11:29:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/the-secret-to-israels-success-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-1d00-da43-afdf-3f229bc00000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫郊区发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人死亡，两人受伤；恐怖分子被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-two-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-suspect-shot-dead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</link><description>一名66岁的妇女当场被宣布死亡，一名80多岁的男子在医院伤重不治身亡；以色列警方称袭击者是来自约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 10:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-two-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-suspect-shot-dead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</guid></item><item><title>绝望的加沙人向 GoFundMe 寻求帮助。它并不总是有回报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/desperate-gazans-turned-to-gofundme-for-help-it-didnt-always-pay-off/00000191-08ff-dc1a-a1b7-19ff56ee0000</link><description>数以万计的巴勒斯坦人利用众筹网站筹集了重要资金，以帮助他们生存或逃离加沙地带。但有些人面临着剥削、繁文缛节、限制和延误，这可能是生死攸关的问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/desperate-gazans-turned-to-gofundme-for-help-it-didnt-always-pay-off/00000191-08ff-dc1a-a1b7-19ff56ee0000</guid></item></channel></rss>